description:
The investment seeks to provide investment results that, before fees and expenses, track the price and yield performance of the Military Veterans Index (the "index").
 The fund will normally invest at least 80% of its total assets in securities of the index. The index is designed to measure the performance of a portfolio of large and mid-capitalization U.S. stocks of companies with policies and practices determined to be Military Friendly®, as indicated by VIQTORY's list of Military Friendly® Employers.
